Oct 2 (Reuters) - The following financial services industry appointments were announced on Thursday. To inform us of other job changes, email moves@thomsonreuters.com.

INVESTMENT SYNERGY GROUP GMBH (ISG) The Germany-based energy trading firm has expanded its emissions trading desk with the hiring of ex-ABN AMRO carbon trader Peter de Waal. [ID:nL6N0RX1Y1]  STANDARD CHARTERED PLC <STAN.L> The company said it appointed Richard Pattle as vice chairman of its private banking clients division. [ID:nL3N0RX1QG]  DEUTSCHE ASSET & WEALTH MANAGEMENT (DEUTSCHE AWM)